THE FORUM, the ideas programme with BRIDGET KENDALL. Sociologist LORD ANTHONY GIDDENS on how to fight climate change. Nigerian novelist and poet BEN OKRI on breaking free. American anthropologist SARAH HRDY on sharing parenting.